observations.recommendation:
We recommended the Municipal Mayor to direct the Municipal Accountant to:

a. Prioritize the reconciliation and evaluation of available records and secure additional documents within 60 days from receipt thereof to establish the updated status of the balances of the fund transfers particularly those grants with carry over beginning balances;

b. Submit a letter of justification indicating the reason/s of non-utilization of fund transfers totaling P3,512,740.00;

c. Coordinate with the implementing units to assess the needs for those unexpended fund balances from NGAs. Should the funds be proven no longer needed, remit immediately to the SA, but if still needed, request authority to use the fund for other related projects of the Municipality; and

d. Prepare the appropriate adjusting journal entries for the transfer of the grants and donations recognized in the GF book and submit to the Audit Team the corresponding Journal Entry Voucher.
